Hello and thank you for purchasing Dog Chase!\
To download this game you need to extract the zip file. In order to play this game it requires an intel 64 or apple silicon chip.From there, all the files needed are presented and all you need to do to play is to open the exe file named \'91Dog Chase\'92.\
\
After opening the exe file, you will be prompted with a start screen. From there you can click the \'91help\'92 button to look at further gameplay instructions or click the \'91play\'92 button to get to the levels screen. Survival mode has not been unlocked yet and so it is disabled.\
\
From the levels screen for this prototype you will only see that level 1 is unlocked. In further production once you finish the first level the second will unlock and so on.\
