\cf0 After clicking on level 1 you will be brought to the game screen and the player will begin to move. To control the character you use the arrow keys and each key responds to a different direction in which the character will move. Up arrow key being move upwards, right arrow key being move towards the right, left arrow key being move towards the left and down arrow key being move downwards. \
\
To pause the game the player can press the escape button. When the pause menu shows up you have the option to resume the game or to go back to the levels page. You can also press escape to resume the game.\
\
The objective of the levels is to pick up all the dogs and simultaneously avoid hitting the walls and any other obstacles that may be in the way. The dog counter in the upper left corner of the screen will tell you how many dogs you have left to pick up in order to complete that particular level. \
\
Once all the dogs have been collected you will see a congratulations screen popup and have the option to go back to the start screen or go to the next level. However, since there is only one level in this prototype, clicking next level brings you to a screen that says \'91coming soon\'85\'92. This screen also has a button bringing you back to the main menu.\
\
